JsonTransformer

An abstarct class the the controllers inherit from. JSON parsing and stringifying methods are written here.

CostCalculatorController

Gets all the data from the query params, uses CostCalculator to get the data for a response and based on the data creates a response JSON.

GoogleAiController

The constructor takes the target and the webshop as arguments, with these and the private final API key and API url it establishes the connection. The large response JSON of Google maps API is processed here.
